{"id":77389,"title":"[Methods of mathematical modeling in morphological diagnostics of Chernobyl factor influence on the testes of coal miners of Donbas--the Chernobyl disaster fighters].","abstract":"The morphometric estimation of parenchyma and stroma condition included the determination of 29 parameters in testicles at 27 persons. The mathematical model of morphogenesis of testicles was created by Bayes' method. The method of differential diagnosis of testicles tissues' changes conditioned by the influence of the Chernobyl factor and/or unfavorable terms of the work in underground coal mines have been worked out. Its practical use provides exactness and reliability of the diagnosis (not less than 95%), independence from the level of the qualification and personal experience of the doctor, allows us to unify, optimize and individualize the diagnostic algorithms, answer the requirements of evidential medicine.","date":"2014-06-09","categories":"Occupational Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24908955","annotations":[{"name":"Medicine","weight":0.782137,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medicine"},{"name":"Testicle","weight":0.764281,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Testicle"},{"name":"Tissue (biology)","weight":0.557965,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tissue_(biology)"},{"name":"Physician","weight":0.519298,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Physician"},{"name":"Morphology (biology)","weight":0.518773,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Morphology_(biology)"},{"name":"Chernobyl disaster","weight":0.494375,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chernobyl_disaster"},{"name":"Differential diagnosis","weight":0.433237,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Differential_diagnosis"},{"name":"Morphogenesis","weight":0.415136,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Morphogenesis"},{"name":"Parenchyma","weight":0.369348,"wikipedia_